{"tid":2223770,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"共產黨：去信全體公務員呼籲切勿參與明日反共公眾活動","createTime":"2020-09-30T05:27:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-30T05:45:33.000Z","uid":21470,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e1d92b68b53bd034540ac5ce34e6309260aa7110","tid":2223770,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T05:27:47.000Z","msg":"聶德權去信公務員　提醒切忌參與明日非法公眾活動 <br />\n<br />\n公務員事務局長聶德權向公務員發信，指警方已對明天舉行的公眾遊行發出反對通知書，提醒公務員切忌參加任何可能違反限聚令的活動，相信公務員能明辨是非，奉公守法，遵守公務員守則訂定的操守準則，強調政府極為重視公務員的品行操守，對違法公務員是零容忍，絕不姑息。他表示，截至9月底，有46名公務員因涉嫌參加非法公眾活動被捕、現正接受警方調查或正被起訴，全部已被停職。<br />\n<br />\n 聶德權表示，香港過去一年多經歷暴亂及疫情衝擊，在各方努力下，迎來喘息空間，希望作為政府骨幹的公務員團隊，支持特區政府，維持社會安寧，保障市民利益。 <br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2359607\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2359607&d=uIqzu4H250jM%2FFVIgxmQWJB82cw%2Bhl0zMn8EQHxvzrU%3D&h=7c83743f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2359607</a>"},{"pid":"26d2d74ad94ca01b786ecce4b38f8ff8a46da3e4","tid":2223770,"uid":132810,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T05:28:42.000Z","msg":"收嗲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff9071a23045e1ff518fbbe49f43e5b7b7228837","tid":2223770,"uid":52006,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T05:30:16.000Z","msg":"必須姓黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b840653d378b54a3eae0a69b209c7879a5db087","tid":2223770,"uid":56806,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T05:30:3